data.description: Nestled amidst the serene landscape of Tonto Basin, this exquisite property at 296 W Burtons Lane offers a unique blend of luxury and tranquility. Spanning over 6.14 acres of pristine land, you're guaranteed privacy with no possibility of neighbors building close by. The estate boasts a fully-equipped RV hookup, perfect for the adventurous at heart. The grounds are a horticultural delight with multiple fruit trees dotting the landscape, providing both shade and bounty. The residence itself offers phenomenal views of Mount Ord, Four Peaks, and Picture Mountain, ensuring a picturesque backdrop to your daily life. Inside, the home welcomes you with a totally remodeled kitchen, featuring Brazilian granite countertops, a spacious walk-in pantry, and all new appliances. The property also includes horse stalls, catering to equestrian enthusiasts.  Also, the brand-new bridges across Tonto Creek to be finished in June.
